        "Title": "Cleaning Up The Seas",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COASTALTOWN",
        "PublicId": "103044989551",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository b9ad09d2-9555-4f6c-8210-114173410725).Image",
        "Description": "A local wildlife conservation focused nonprofit as recently contacted us with a request. They have received countless complaints about various personnel from Villa Caruso and the accompanying laboratory simply dumping whatever they wish into the nearby sea, putting the lives of the sea life at massive risk. One exceptionally disgruntled fisherman claiming they&apos;re &quot;Killing all the damn fish!&quot; They requested we personally see to it that Karma is properly dished out.\r\rI will leave you to prepare.",
